<http://example.org/rpg-game-character-ontology#> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Ontology> .
<http://example.org/rpg-game-character-ontology#> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/creator> "Yunus Erdem Ocak" .
<http://example.org/rpg-game-character-ontology#> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/creator> "İrem Boyalıoğlu" .
<http://example.org/rpg-game-character-ontology#> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "An OWL/RDF ontology for a small-scale RPG game character and quest knowledge graph, extended in v2 with data acquisition, player behavior events, and recommendation-oriented concepts."@en .
<http://example.org/rpg-game-character-ontology#> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/title> "RPG Game Character Ontology"@en .
<http://example.org/rpg-game-character-ontology#> <http://purl.org/vocab/vann/preferredNamespacePrefix> "rpg" .
<http://example.org/rpg-game-character-ontology#> <http://purl.org/vocab/vann/preferredNamespaceUri> "http://example.org/rpg-game-character-ontology#" .
<http://example.org/rpg-game-character-ontology#> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Version 2 of a small-scale ontology for modeling RPG game characters, quests, items, locations, player behavior events, play styles, and simple recommendations."@en .
<http://example.org/rpg-game-character-ontology#> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "RPG Game Character Ontology"@en .
<http://example.org/rpg-game-character-ontology#> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#versionInfo> "2.0" .
